Class MyWarpPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.plugin.PluginBase
      • org.bukkit.plugin.java.JavaPlugin
        • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.bukkit.MyWarpPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor, org.bukkit.command.TabCompleter, org.bukkit.command.TabExecutor, org.bukkit.plugin.Plugin

    public final class MyWarpPlugin
extends org.bukkit.plugin.java.JavaPlugin
    The MyWarp plugin singleton when running on Bukkit.

    This class is loaded by Bukkit when the plugin is initialized.

      • registerClosable

        protected void registerClosable(java.io.Closeable closeable)
        Registers the given closable for closure when the plugin is disabled.

        Registered Closables will be stored within a WeakReference. If MyWarp is disabled by Bukkit and the reference is still valid, Closeable.close() is invoked.

        Parameters:
        closeable - the Closable to register
